      Thank you for this Ted. The basics concepts are clear and well described and I appreciate the specific examples. I think folks are so excited about the possibility of some top down action that it could be easy to lose focus on the absolute necessity for bottom up creativity and initiative. The current administration has some great experience and infrastructure built around bottom up work. The challenge is, of course, that it was initiated through an electoral process that is steeped in partisanship whatever our best intentions. The conversation about how to move beyond those beginnings to become a truly inclusive bottom up effort is a very important one. 

                  
    </td>
  </tr>


